DOC.brief_summary: The investigator intends to review retrospective de-identified data of patients who have had Open, Laparoscopic, Ureteroscopic or Percutaneous Urologic Surgery.
DOC.brief_title: Chart Review of Those Who Have Had Open, Laparoscopic, Ureteroscopic, or Percutaneous Surgery
DOC.detailed_description: The investigator reviews retrospective de-identified data of patients who have had Open, Laparoscopic, Ureteroscopic or Percutaneous Urologic Surgery in order to determine different clinical or operative issues.
DOC.criteria: Patients must have had Open, Laparoscopic, Ureteroscopic or Percutaneous Urologic Surgery at UCIMC Department of Urology
